Just had my first eye check at @owndays_sg 👓
I learned so much about the lenses they carry including progressive lenses. They are made to help people aged 40 and above see near, far and intermediate distances so you don’t have to switch between multiple spectacles (take note because you and I probably need them in future!)
Plus, I found the cutest frames while I was there 😍
If you haven’t gotten your eyes checked this year, this is your sign! Visit OWNDAYS for a free eye check and enjoy free progressive lenses with any spectacles purchase starting from just $98
AND get a FREE bottle of lens cleaner when you flash this post.
